==Finnish==
===Noun, obscene===

A [[whore]] or [[harlot]], a [[prostitute]].

More obscene if used meaning a female person who has lots of sexual activity with other people, regardless of their gender, but doesn't bill for her service.

Even more obscene if you call a female person huora if they're not one at all.

REALLY obscene if you use it about any male person (as good as, or even worse than calling them [[hintti]], regardless of their sexual preferences). 

Sometimes used more or less humorously to refer to a person who can be bought to do anything.

Finnish synonyms: [[portto]], [[ilotyttö]], [[prostituoitu]]

